Package webfx.devs

package webfx.devs
  • Class
    Description
    Data
    The Data class is an extension of a HashMap<String, Object> and so all HashMap operations can be performed on it.
    Database
    A simple SQLite-based database utility class designed to work with POJOs for schema generation and data insertion.
    DataManager
    A utility class for working with Data Objects.
    Endpoint
    The Annotation interface that is meant for establishing endpoints
    Ignore
    Used in classes that are meant to be treated as tables for a database.
    Nullable
    Used in classes that are meant to be treated as tables for a database.
    ResourceManager
    A utility class that is used to retrieve and manipulate resources.
    Router
    This is the Router class which can be used to navigate between different pages.
    TemplateEngine
    The main class that runs the lightweight TemplateEngine.
